snippet.title: Cats Organized Neatly Trailer
snippet.description:
Cats Organized Neatly on Steam: [https://store.steampowered.com/app/1369340/Cats_Organized_Neatly/]
Hey Poor Player Cats Organized Neatly Review: [https://www.heypoorplayer.com/2020/12/15/cats-organized-neatly-review-pc/]

In this 2D puzzle game you have the responsibility to arrange your feline friends in a way that fits the grid. Cats Organized Neatly comes with 80 different handcrafted levels and a whole bunch of cats in all shapes and sizes.

Cats Organized Neatly was developed and self-published by indie team DU&I.
